===性能影響===

PassMark Software在2008年進行了一個測試，發現2.0版本對電腦性能的影響很少，相對於其他測試的防毒軟件平均影響為低。<ref>{{cite web | last=Wren | first=David | coauthors=Fryer, Michael | title=Antivirus & Internet Security products Performance Benchmarking | url=http://www.passmark.com/ftp/antivirus-performance-testing-vista-ed2.pdf | date=June 6, 2008 | work= | publisher=PassMark Software Pty Ltd | accessdate=2009-06-02 | archive-date=2008-12-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204104806/http://www.passmark.com/ftp/antivirus-performance-testing-vista-ed2.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>賽門鐵克資助了這個測試及提供了一些腳本作基準測試。<ref name="Pass">{{cite web | last=Lai | first=Karen | coauthors=Wren, David | title=Antivirus, Internet Security and Total Security Performance Benchmarking Edition 3 | url=http://www.passmark.com/ftp/antivirus_09-performance-testing-ed3.pdf | date=February 6, 2009 | work=Antivirus, Internet Security, and Total Security Performance Benchmarking | publisher=PassMark Software Pty Ltd | accessdate=2009-06-01 | archive-date=2009-08-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806195929/http://www.passmark.com/ftp/antivirus_09-performance-testing-ed3.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>系統以乾淨安裝的Windows Vista作基準測試，然後再安裝一個安全套裝。<ref name="Pass" />

